OL,6,FA Guernsey production of The Good Life
OL,7,Fwill be brought to life with the help
OL,8,Fof a real goat.
OL,10,FOpening on Tuesday 18 June, the
OL,11,Fproduction is about the Good couple
OL,12,Fdeciding to become self-sufficient in
OL,13,Ftheir London home.
OL,15,FBut rather than using a puppet to play
OL,16,Fthe Good family's goat, the production
OL,17,Fhas enlisted the help of 14-month-old
OL,18,FKit.
