OL,4,CGuernsey stage
OL,6,FKit will play Geraldine, who is bought
OL,7,Fby the Goods to provide them with milk
OL,8,Fand fertiliser.
OL,10,FChris Bougourd, who plays Tom Good in
OL,11,Fthe production, came up with the idea
OL,12,Fof using a live farm animal.
OL,14,FHe explained: "The UK production used
OL,15,Fa puppet goat, but come on, it's
OL,16,FGuernsey!
OL,18,F"We've got some beautiful goats on the
OL,19,Fisland, and it would be sacrilege not
OL,20,Fto use a Guernsey golden goat on
OL,21,Fstage."
