OL,3,CKit the goat makes his debut on a
OL,4,CGuernsey stage
OL,6,FThe mild-mannered Kit is actually
OL,7,FGeraldine's understudy, as the
OL,8,Foriginal goat was 'butt out' after
OL,9,Fbeing, in Chris' words, "quite
OL,10,Fnaughty" with "a bit of an attitude".
OL,12,FMichelle Cox's daughter owns Kit. She
OL,13,Fexplained: "Chris said it would be
OL,14,Fsomething really different and
OL,15,Fsomething that the audience isn't
OL,16,Fgoing to see all the time.
OL,18,F"(My daughter) is quite excited about
OL,19,Fit, and said she'd love to see Kit on
OL,20,Fstage.
